                <div class="eyebrow" data-label="Business">Business</div>
                <h1 class="lede-text-only__hed"><span class="lede-text-only__highlight">Britain’s Small Businesses Aren’t Prepared for Brexit</span></h1>
                <div class="lede-text-only__dek">
                <span class="lede-text-only__highlight">
                    <p>As the big divorce looms, they have no idea what the rules will be or what they’ll have to do to adapt.</p>
                </span>
            </div>
        
                <address class="lede-text-only__byline">By <div class="author">Stefania Spezzati
        <div class="author__modal">
            <a class="author__modal-social" data-feed="twitter" href="https://www.twitter.com/stespezzati" target="_blank" aria-label="Follow Stefania Spezzati on Twitter (opens in new window)">@stespezzati</a>
            
            <a class="author__modal-bio" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/authors/ARO82jWldvY/stefania-spezzati" rel="author">More stories by Stefania Spezzati</a>
        </div>
    </div> and <div class="author">Charlie Devereux
        <div class="author__modal">
            <a class="author__modal-social" data-feed="twitter" href="https://www.twitter.com/charliedevereux" target="_blank" aria-label="Follow Charlie Devereux on Twitter (opens in new window)">@charliedevereux</a>
            
            <a class="author__modal-bio" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/authors/AQD-13RapqM/charlie-devereux" rel="author">More stories by Charlie Devereux</a>
        </div>
    </div></address>
                <div class="lede-text-only__times">
                    
