            </a></div>
            <div class="share-article-button__option"><a href="mailto:?subject=Britain%E2%80%99s%20Small%20Businesses%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20Prepared%20for%20Brexit%20-%20Bloomberg&body=Britain%E2%80%99s%20Small%20Businesses%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20Prepared%20for%20Brexit%0D%0A%0D%0Aby%20Stefania%20Spezzati%20and%20Charlie%20Devereux%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20big%20divorce%20looms%2C%20they%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20the%20rules%20will%20be%20or%20what%20they%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20do%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-03-08%2Fbritain-s-small-businesses-aren-t-prepared-for-the-big-divorce" class="share-article-button__link" rel="nofollow" onclick="dataLayer.push({
        'event': 'article_social_share',
        'eventCategory': 'social',
        'eventAction': 'share',
